snippet: San Diego will pay $250,000 to a woman who claimed she was sexually harassed by former Mayor Bob Filner.
abstract: San Diego will pay $250,000 to Irene McCormack Jackson, woman who claimed she was sexually harassed by former Mayor Bob Filner; settlement ends lawsuit, but harassment suits by two more women are pending.
lead_paragraph: San Diego will pay $250,000 to a woman who claimed she was sexually harassed by former Mayor Bob Filner.

headline.main: California: San Diego Settles One Suit Against Ex-Mayor
headline.print_headline: California: San Diego Settles One Suit Against Ex-Mayor
